 F.</span> <span property="familyName">Hahn</span>, <span property="honorificSuffix">MD, PhD</span></div><div class="content"><div class="affiliations"><div property="affiliation" typeof="Organization"><span property="name">From the Department of Radiology, Division of Abdominal Imaging and Intervention (O.A.C., A.H.S., R.N.U., P.F.H., D.V.S.), and Department of Surgery (C.R.F.), Massachusetts General Hospital, 55 Fruit St, WHT 270, Boston, MA 02114. Presented as an education exhibit at the 2006 RSNA Annual Meeting. Received May 4, 2007; revision requested June 15 and received June 29; accepted July 3. D.V.S. receives research support from General Electric and consults for the Bracco Group; all other authors have no financial relationships to disclose.</span></div></div><div class="core-author-link"><a href="/authored-by/Hahn/Peter+F" rel="nofollow">View all articles by this author</a></div></div></div><div id="con5" property="author" typeof="Person"><div class="heading"><span property="givenName">Cristina R.</span> <span property="familyName">Ferrone</span>, <span property="honorificSuffix">MD</span></div><div class="content"><div class="affiliations"><div property="affiliation" typeof="Organization"><span property="name">From the Department of Radiology, Division of Abdominal Imaging and Intervention (O.A.C., A.H.S., R.N.U., P.F.H., D.V.S.), and Department of Surgery (C.R.F.), Massachusetts General Hospital, 55 Fruit St, WHT 270, Boston, MA 02114. Presented as an education exhibit at the 2006 RSNA Annual Meeting. Received May 4, 2007; revision requested June 15 and received June 29; accepted July 3. D.V.S. receives research support from General Electric and consults for the Bracco Group; all other authors have no financial relationships to disclose.</span></div></div><div class="core-author-link"><a href="/authored-by/Ferrone/Cristina+R" rel="nofollow">View all articles by this author</a></div></div></div><div id="con6" property="author" typeof="Person"><div class